description:
#farewell #remembered #doubledash downright instead of rightdash for up to 0.2 timesave. 
make sure to not downright on the frame after bopping the fish or else you will very likely hit it a second time.
for the part after the fish bop, you can downleft instead of dashing straight down to make the fishboost easier, but in my experience that makes getting a clean landing at the end harder (and saves less time)
